{"tid":664600,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[會員齊參與]LIHKG香港女神聯賽 17-18 女神清算大會","createTime":"2018-05-14T07:59:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-14T08:07:15.000Z","uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a791bbf634f31549268e4bde2aea31dac324eb19","tid":664600,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T07:59:44.000Z","msg":"以下女神於2017-18季度聯賽中積分處於極低水平,全季分數高於0分但不足15分,根據賽制需接受清算大會查核,由會員投票決定有關女神應否繼續於來季作賽<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2017-18 LIHKG港超女神聯賽<br />\n第15位 趙慧珊 30戰 3勝0和27負 得9分<br />\n(若清算投票獲通過,冠聯將會產生一個新出缺)<br />\n<br />\n2017-18 LIHKG港冠女神聯賽<br />\n第18位 黃心美 34戰 4勝0和30負 得12分<br />\n(若清算投票獲通過,冠聯將會產生一個新出缺)<br />\n<br />\n2017-18 LIHKG港甲女神聯賽<br />\n第17位 郭藹明 34戰 3勝0和31負 得9分<br />\n(若清算投票獲通過,冠聯將會產生一個新出缺)<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n呢三個成績嚴重欠佳既女神會接受清算大會考驗<br />\n不過我地都仲有少少人情味既,接住落黎既三個回覆<br />\n我地會貼三張有關女神既相片出黎,如果大家覺得無情講既就按正評<br />\n如果大家覺得可以放佢一馬,咁就撳負評啦<br />\n至於佢地呢個情形要點樣先至Byebye或者無事,公平起見我會貼晒三個回覆先講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大家踴躍參與<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc24fd93367ff5be3dc75369c921038b4bfbec48","tid":664600,"uid":92376,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T08:00:00.000Z","msg":"趙慧珊<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Mwc1lrd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FMwc1lrd.png&h=21599128&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/nYtbhf5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FnYtbhf5.png&h=21537467&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/9ZvDGur.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F9ZvDGur.png&h=540e4fe2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n無得留低 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可以留低 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85e80bf51f8a56f781c9260521f947591098